data.description: Enjoy the tranquility of waterfront living wrapped by the serene embrace of mature trees. Quick and easy access to major cities for work and entertainment. This exceptional property offers the perfect blend of luxury, space, and natural beauty. It's an oasis of comfort and style, perfect for those seeking a peaceful retreat without sacrificing convenience. The third floor reveals a delightful surprise with two bonus rooms, a full bath, and a kitchenette. With no burdensome HOA fees and the assurance of no flood concerns, this property represents a rare opportunity to transform this oasis into your forever home. *This home is available for showings although a 1st right of refusal contingency exists.*
